query:
INSERT INTO projects (
                id, organization_id, name, color,
                created_at, updated_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            RETURNING
                id               AS "id!: Uuid",
                organization_id  AS "organization_id!: Uuid",
                name             AS "name!",
                color            AS "color!",
                created_at       AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at       AS "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
